latestPosts.caption:
MEDAL MONDAY 🥇 3:27:10

Chicago marathon was an absolute vibe! The city, runners and crowd was electric. World major star No. ⭐️⭐️

I might not have hit my 3:15 goal, however I’m incredibly proud of myself for staying in the fight and hitting a 12min PR. Need to figure out how to stop taking the long route 🤣

Felt so good until mile 19 but started feeling cramps coming on. The cramps caught at mile 23/24 and it was a fight to the finish line.

This COMMUNITY and sport has CHANGED my life ⚡️ Congratulations to everyone that ran — 26.2 miles is an incredible accomplishment 🎉

#running #runner #run #chicago #marathon #chicagomarathon #runners #worldmajormarathon #runningcommunity
